          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2012-07-04 04:21:38.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-56 ptlrpc: post rqbd with flag LNET_INS_LOCAL",
        "message": "LU-56 ptlrpc: post rqbd with flag LNET_INS_LOCAL\n\nLNet has a new flag LNET_INS_LOCAL which can be used by CPT\naffinity threads while posting buffer.\n(commit 279bbc81e03dc74d273ec12b4d9e703ca94404c4)\nBuffer posted with this flag will be attached on local partition\nonly, and LND threads can find/match buffer by grabbing a local\npartition lock which is good for performance.\nThis patch applied this flag to ptlrpc service.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I75cee15f125b033642195a71921dbc6ad4db5dfd\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
